onderland (  1865 ) and Through the Looking Glass (  1872 ), who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Alice de Stonor was born about 1332, in Shropshire, England, United Kingdom, her father, Thomas de Stonor, was 27 and her mother, Alice de Lisle, was 23. She married John Coningsby about 1352, in Alcester, Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"Abt 1332–Deceased":"umbes 1332–Surnud","1332–Female":"1332–Surnud","1323–1362":"1323–1362","1360–1445":"1360–1445","1306–1382":"1306–1382","1310–Female":"1310–Surnud","1445":"1445","1323":"1323","Abt 1332":"umbes 1332","1310":"1310","1332":"1332","1362":"1362","1382":"1382","1360":"1360","1306":"1306","Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shropshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1332–Deceased":"noin 1332–Kuollut","1332–Female":"1332–Kuollut","1323–1362":"1323–1362","1360–1445":"1360–1445","1306–1382":"1306–1382","1310–Female":"1310–Kuollut","1445":"1445","1323":"1323","Abt 1332":"noin 1332","1310":"1310","1332":"1332","1362":"1362","1382":"1382","1360":"1360","1306":"1306","Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shropshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1332–Deceased":"environ 1332–Décédée","1332–Female":"1332–Décédée","1323–1362":"1323–1362","1360–1445":"1360–1445","1306–1382":"1306–1382","1310–Female":"1310–Décédée","1445":"1445","1323":"1323","Abt 1332":"environ 1332","1310":"1310","1332":"1332","1362":"1362","1382":"1382","1360":"1360","1306":"1306","Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Alice de Stonor est née environ 1332, à Shropshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Thomas de Stonor, avait 27 ans et sa mère, Alice de Lisle, avait 23 ans. Elle a épousé John Coningsby en